              <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2021/10/11/13/12/qr-code-6701489_1280.png" alt="Master QR Badge" class="qr-image img-fluid mb-4">
              <h4>Master Access Badge</h4>
              <p class="mb-4">This QR code provides administrative access to the Smart Digital Product Support Desk system.</p>
              <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn btn-primary" id="download-badge"><i class="fas fa-download me-2"></i> Download Badge</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <div class="card h-100">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="mb-4">Badge Usage Instructions</h4>
                
                <div class="mb-4">
                  <h5><i class="fas fa-lock me-2"></i> Security</h5>
                  <p>This QR code contains encrypted credentials that grant administrative access to your support system. Keep it secure and share only with authorized personnel.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mb-4">
                  <h5><i class="fas fa-qrcode me-2"></i> Scanning</h5>
                  <p>Use any standard QR scanner or the Smart Support mobile app to scan this code. The system will authenticate your credentials automatically.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mb-4">
                  <h5><i class="fas fa-sync-alt me-2"></i> Refreshing</h5>
                  <p>For security purposes, this QR code refreshes every 30 days. Return to this page to download the latest version when needed.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                  <h5><i class="fas fa-user-shield me-2"></i> Permissions</h5>
                  <p>Scanning this badge grants full administrative rights including access to sensitive customer data, system settings, and advanced analytics.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
